  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01213', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關皮爾森（Pearson）相關係數和斯皮爾曼（Spearman）相關係數的敘述，下列何者最合適？', '["都適合用來評估兩個次序變數（ordinalvariable）之間的相關性", "當皮爾森相關係數為0.25，統計檢定p值<0.0001，表示兩個變數之間有弱相關", "當資料有極端值（extremevalue）時，使用皮爾森相關係數較為合適", "當皮爾森相關係數為0，表示兩個連續變數之間不具有線性或其他形式的關聯"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01214', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據某職業棒球隊投手過去的經驗，練投50顆球，投進好球帶的次數為40顆。假設每次投 球都是獨立的，倘若該投手今天練投10顆球，有9顆球以上投進好球帶的機率為何？', '["0.375", "0.107", "0.268", "4.198×10-6"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01215', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '調查某醫院住院病人的住院日數，發現平均值是10天，中位數是8天，在全部住院病人中， 住院6天的人數最多，資料為單峰分布。下列敘述何者正確？', '["可能有一些病人住院特別久", "標準差是2天", "住院日數符合常態分布", "大約50%的病人住院少於6天"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
